import React from 'react';

export default props => (
	<form className="form-inline">
	  <input type="text" className="form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2 col-1" id="inlineFormInput1" placeholder="ID"/>
	  <input type="text" className="form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2" id="inlineFormInput2" placeholder="FirstName"/>
	  <input type="text" className="form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2" id="inlineFormInput3" placeholder="LastName"/>
	  <input type="text" className="form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2" id="inlineFormInput4" placeholder="Email"/>
	  <input type="text" className="form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2" id="inlineFormInput5" placeholder="Phone"/>

	  <button type="submit" className="btn btn-primary mb-2">Submit</button>
	</form>
)
